---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Juegos y Apps | Toby on Fitness Tech"
  description="Juega nuestros juegos de fitness y prueba nuestras apps de entrenamiento, sin necesidad de descargar nada."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-neutral-950 text-white py-12 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          🎮 Juegos y Apps
        </h1>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-lg">
          Juega nuestros juegos de fitness y prueba nuestras apps de entrenamiento, sin necesidad de descargar nada.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-4">🕹️ Juegos</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10">
        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">MMA RPG</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 En vivo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Un RPG de peleas de MMA por turnos. Crea tu peleador, domina combinaciones y sube de rango.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Pelea</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">RPG</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Estrategia</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://tobyonfitnesstech.com/mma-rpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            ▶ Jugar ahora
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Gridbound Realms</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 En vivo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Un juego de estrategia táctica por cuadrícula. Comanda tus unidades y conquista el reino.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Estrategia</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Táctica</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Cuadrícula</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://tobyonfitnesstech.com/gridbound-realms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            ▶ Jugar ahora
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500 mb-4">📱 Apps</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">BJJ Buddy</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 En vivo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Haz seguimiento de tu entrenamiento de BJJ, registra tus rounds, monitorea tu progreso y mejora tu grappling.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">BJJ</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Registro de entrenamiento</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Progreso</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://tobyonfitnesstech.com/bjj-buddy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            🥋 Abrir app
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-neutral-900 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 p-6 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 mb-3">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">NutriTrack</h3>
            <span class="text-sm px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-900/40 border border-green-500/40 text-green-300">🟢 En vivo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Seguimiento nutricional gratuito. Registra tus comidas, cumple tus macros y alimenta tu entrenamiento.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Nutrición</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Macros</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-neutral-300 bg-neutral-800 rounded-full px-3 py-1">Registro de comidas</span>
          </div>
          <a href="https://tobyonfitnesstech.com/nutritrack" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-3 rounded-xl bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 transition-colors font-semibold">
            🥗 Abrir app
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
